        <p>
            Digital technology has changed the way the food and beverage industry uses and operates its resources. The technologies such as IoT, data analytics, cloud, and smart sensors have the potential to transform the food and beverage industry. A growing number of companies are gathering data about changing the business atmosphere and reevaluating how the processes, resources and labour force will operate in the future. The smart sensors will collect the data taken from the equipment, send it to the IT system for analysis and give an invaluable lesson on how to improve equipment operation and make it energy efficient. 
